methods.name: create_app
methods.desc: Initialize the marketplace with an agricultural product and price per unit.

methods.name: update_price
methods.desc: Allows the owner to update the price of the product.

methods.name: update_min_quantity
methods.desc: Allows the owner to update the minimum order quantity.

methods.name: setup_marketplace
methods.desc: Sets up the marketplace with necessary funding and registers to receive products.

methods.name: help_buyer_register
methods.desc: Helps a buyer register to receive the product if they haven't already.

methods.name: purchase
methods.desc: Allows users to buy the product by sending the correct payment.

methods.name: buy_with_registration
methods.desc: Allows users to buy the product with automatic registration if needed.

methods.name: restock_product
methods.desc: Allows the owner to restock the product.

methods.name: close_marketplace
methods.desc: Allows the owner to close the marketplace and reclaim assets.
